{"tid":330530,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母臭閪,個喉嚨發炎完未呀！！！！！！","createTime":"2017-07-21T09:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T05:48:58.000Z","uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"828fc039768810dad764cb087ad0f91a464ae045","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"仆你個街總共痛柒左2個星期<br />\n屌你老母本身淨喉嚨發炎<br />\n點柒知感染埋扁桃腺<br />\n佢老味d醫生食屎大<br />\n你老味開5日抗生素,2日感冒藥<br />\n一開頭諗著食哂d抗生素,乖乖地戒下就冇事<br />\n喂食撚哂,冇料到既？<br />\n仲要比之前仲痛,又周身痛<br />\n搞到我要睇2個醫生<br />\n洗左勁多錢睇個19喉嚨<br />\n第一個醫生同我回水呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n汁柒左佢呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回水回水回水</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">回水回水回水</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">回水</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">回水回水</span>"},{"pid":"8ff00df630c504bb766682d28d75c5b89603967c","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母汁柒左佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e51282e081eeefea508cc21fcf633da1473bea1","tid":330530,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"357dc56e7c106c670e96a8b418836c38944e6de2","tid":330530,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:22:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27339cf0fc95ca5ce3c5a7696e351db38357271","tid":330530,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2d7b45d9d8fcadbd8c32f1b0fa566d3ad326b9d","tid":330530,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/192814_0fd447ebbe34aa906536195599f56d2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F192814_0fd447ebbe34aa906536195599f56d2c.jpg&h=e7030771&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d43983d16841b17605857bb7efe634d4796f6d1c","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3d05fd6cf25aac6abe921e79d3b3aee6171cc9","tid":330530,"uid":37281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T00:54:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce834c6fbcc94360580213df69719b90710ef91e","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:12:10.000Z","msg":"求救"},{"pid":"2d4e655d5d930e14d675b8a6f9c38b99b41c2393","tid":330530,"uid":75667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:14:04.000Z","msg":"中藥三日搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b1b6b4e374c4487297e4a7d2dffd0aa8fea745","tid":330530,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食極唔好，屌，食咁撚多消炎食到個胃爛，痛撚到仆街"},{"pid":"36fce434d41805b9c9c6ee5d6988ce629393cc0a","tid":330530,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:16:36.000Z","msg":"血癌都係咁上下徵兆 巴打checkcheck好啲"},{"pid":"3729d68d44d5794b867660d7212409296a59d38c","tid":330530,"uid":126512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁<br />\n去公立醫院排急症食左一個星期無事"},{"pid":"ae4c24bd1d769daa82fd9f518ce265d1460e047b","tid":330530,"uid":201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:22:50.000Z","msg":"我又係,睇完醫生食左消炎藥就開始胃痛,痛到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a46fe53557d30d303fa0dd20d4e25de2db0724c","tid":330530,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"下世唔好食錯藥"},{"pid":"ebb227568adbf880500b9101c72e9f7c166f26f7","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhelp"},{"pid":"391c6535a240c376be000efbeb78b5dab88fe0a1","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhelp</blockquote><br />\n試下中醫樓上話"},{"pid":"3b9791ad98f40b04bd64d29e187444630d8f93bd","tid":330530,"uid":126847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:17:48.000Z","msg":"羅漢果"},{"pid":"aae48aa04e7ec47e14dfb16fb7719701dafe898b","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhelp</blockquote><br />\n試下中醫樓上話</blockquote><br />\n中西藥一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你點呀"},{"pid":"bbc38c1ad3f3744b4ee41a33ce9c0b21533e2ac8","tid":330530,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:32:04.000Z","msg":"而家睇緊醫生留名.....一陣買巴打講既維他命B"},{"pid":"b30fe75cc281c826360c463acfb1b2479fda9f23","tid":330530,"uid":122601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"之前洗左2舊7 睇喉嚨發炎同發燒得2日藥 , 最後發燒無左 , 喉嚨發炎仲係到 , 最後洗多600幾睇個貴醫生問5日藥先好番"},{"pid":"adf2cb8898868bfa3c705da4e5fddfb02786fe43","tid":330530,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"流感高峰期<br />\n大部分感冒都係病毒感染<br />\n你食完一打抗生素都冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗生素係殺細菌唔係殺病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be3ba16ee88270f8afee5ff048ebeb22b73bf9b4","tid":330530,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>流感高峰期<br />\n大部分感冒都係病毒感染<br />\n你食完一打抗生素都冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗生素係殺細菌唔係殺病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而且抗生素通常都係醫生驚你有併發症先開俾你<br />\n主要用途唔係醫好你本身嗰個病<br />\n係預防越來越多病"},{"pid":"914f7d1905c469fc0404f6bdb4401f3848847d57","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhelp</blockquote><br />\n試下中醫樓上話</blockquote><br />\n中西藥一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你點呀</blockquote><br />\n啱啱去睇左中醫<br />\n建議食完d西藥先好睇中醫"},{"pid":"20d143f29a24251c27369e1c75b903014c9dc6a7","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前洗左2舊7 睇喉嚨發炎同發燒得2日藥 , 最後發燒無左 , 喉嚨發炎仲係到 , 最後洗多600幾睇個貴醫生問5日藥先好番</blockquote><br />\n我已經睇多次貴醫生<br />\n都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一起身個喉嚨就好撚乾同痛"},{"pid":"ad0f96e1d41f954f072eeea375f0bef178091893","tid":330530,"uid":51507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"之前都試過痛左成個月<br />\n睇咩醫生食咩藥都冇用<br />\n之後瘋狂飲熱暖水 狂飲個隻 之後就好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e8ea9ec97f36ca500ffc1917c09b8db12984e0","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhelp</blockquote><br />\n試下中醫樓上話</blockquote><br />\n中西藥一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主你點呀</blockquote><br />\n啱啱去睇左中醫<br />\n建議食完d西藥先好睇中醫</blockquote><br />\n仆街都係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860550e9ea25f3170f857c1d8b5ed98d285baa67","tid":330530,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前洗左2舊7 睇喉嚨發炎同發燒得2日藥 , 最後發燒無左 , 喉嚨發炎仲係到 , 最後洗多600幾睇個貴醫生問5日藥先好番</blockquote><br />\n我已經睇多次貴醫生<br />\n都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一起身個喉嚨就好撚乾同痛</blockquote><br />\n呢樣嘢基本上食藥唔會好<br />\n最多都係開paradol俾你止痛"},{"pid":"a06e7502f48bb942421bf6263d2064d7a788ae87","tid":330530,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前洗左2舊7 睇喉嚨發炎同發燒得2日藥 , 最後發燒無左 , 喉嚨發炎仲係到 , 最後洗多600幾睇個貴醫生問5日藥先好番</blockquote><br />\n我已經睇多次貴醫生<br />\n都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次一起身個喉嚨就好撚乾同痛</blockquote><br />\n呢樣嘢基本上食藥唔會好<br />\n最多都係開paradol俾你止痛</blockquote><br />\n話時話其實通常傷風感冒一 兩個禮拜度就會自己好<br />\n所以其實可能唔關醫生事<br />\n係你自己醫好咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173f7f02d4fce7ee828a3f152f392d165f01669e","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"買左blackmore vit b<br />\n<br />\n我個喉嚨係爛撚晒生晒膿呀仆街"},{"pid":"02d5e98ffb94137e36bd9ee3207f7fd3e7d8fa48","tid":330530,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"補下b2 la"},{"pid":"1cef47cf2a5ad84ce6b243d8fa9ddd39846ddd0e","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"好痛，成個喉嚨一照都係黃膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad367fbcd6628ab13f63f4231c29d918d1b81cab","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好痛，成個喉嚨一照都係黃膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完d 19中藥肚瀉<br />\n都冇撚好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad76902576d26d8afec4f60eab8f8f3fb285b24","tid":330530,"uid":88829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"可能Viral infection <br />\n靠自己immune system"},{"pid":"21a6320d6182d23c9c61849c5fe0fec9b20c063e","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能Viral infection <br />\n靠自己immune system</blockquote><br />\n姐係食乜藥都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a793195c6dd45f9a4e5c6ca334621225b4217f","tid":330530,"uid":67054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係咁，食完抗生素就喉嚨勁痛，懷疑係d抗生素會對扁桃腺發炎，我最尾自己買藥房買消炎藥，any type is ok,  一日3/4 果d,  食1 q已經鬆左好多，食2-3 日冇晒事，期間熱氣野唔好食，多飲水"},{"pid":"7f7eccb7e88651db0345847823c58c1a144b3533","tid":330530,"uid":75500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:49:32.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上星期日開始發燒 後尾星期一睇完醫生 食左兩日藥發燒退左 喉嚨仲係痛到仆街<br />\n我自己照入去望仲見到有白色珍珠<br />\n食咩藥先會好架 求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3176a870ed031e1f9dc69e3c32ccef39371b932","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>救命救命<br />\n<br />\n前幾日發燒感冒，食左藥連抗生素，退左燒，點知過兩日喉嚨開始爛，兩邊生晒膿，依家吞口水好似中槍咁，睇多次醫生，佢開多一隻抗生俾我打孖食<br />\n<br />\n乖乖戒口食藥多飲水加用鹽水漱口<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他野可以做<br />\n<br />\n訓一弭就痛得滯紮醒左，好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係咁，食完抗生素就喉嚨勁痛，懷疑係d抗生素會對扁桃腺發炎，我最尾自己買藥房買消炎藥，any type is ok,  一日3/4 果d,  食1 q已經鬆左好多，食2-3 日冇晒事，期間熱氣野唔好食，多飲水</blockquote><br />\n仆街冇食醫生個d傷風藥又打黑痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前就係食消炎藥冇用去至睇醫生"},{"pid":"87399d991ebeba6768aeae03c1c0fa12d4fab40e","tid":330530,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"抗生素好似靜係對Virus有效<br />\n普通傷風唔係virus引起（好似係）"},{