mal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前都係咁，食完抗生素就喉嚨勁痛，懷疑係d抗生素會對扁桃腺發炎，我最尾自己買藥房買消炎藥，any type is ok,  一日3/4 果d,  食1 q已經鬆左好多，食2-3 日冇晒事，期間熱氣野唔好食，多飲水</blockquote><br />\n我都有食醫生開既消炎止痛架<br />\n<br />\np.s. 我割左扁桃腺，有冇關係<br />\n<br />\n琴晚訓左十幾粒鐘，每朝起身都期望會有好轉，點知都係冇，屌"},{"pid":"cd6f558c7fb14cb01689b0e49db8672f6062ad2f","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"好痛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78cf8be8492992cb24d208413c3b3a500088875","tid":330530,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"食完維他命b飛滋都少生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44296f7793f06bf655a856ea62f852cb98e3d644","tid":330530,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"朝朝一起身都痕同痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪關冷氣事"},{"pid":"ec8715a3ed396fb4f8ddcf7534da5216c2ac96c2","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"一覺醒來，仍未好轉，仲係成個喉嚨都係膿<br />\n<br />\n喉膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲食緊抗生素"},{"pid":"8d08f41147b0b2f5d349438e19146eb00dafdbc9","tid":330530,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一覺醒來，仍未好轉，仲係成個喉嚨都係膿<br />\n<br />\n喉膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲食緊抗生素</blockquote><br />\n我決定放棄再睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n友佢算鳩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfdfe93b313f4b1d28fd5688b498d99e5dbbe8f","tid":330530,"uid":20134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"琴晚同個老中醫傾計<br />\n佢以前係大陸做西醫先既<br />\n又係有個病人做完手術之後個口腔爛同發炎得好勁<br />\n佢本身係