" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係你呢d人搞到病菌有抗藥性 無抗生素用到"},{"pid":"fc17885fd5438a5d27803728549810e3e27cc8d2","tid":330530,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:31:53.000Z","msg":"睇西醫食藥係唔會幫你病好<br />\n藥只係禁住你既病徵 eg. 鼻水 <br />\n等你無咁辛苦（抗生素殺菌除外）<br />\n休息多d 飲多d水 開大個窗<br />\n身體抗體殺死病毒/菌<br />\n就會早d病好"},{"pid":"49aa620ce2d931a8979799c4ccc4580e97147a27","tid":330530,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抗生素差兩次先食晒，唔想再食<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有嚴重副作用<br />\n<br />\n我梗係覺得個喉嚨同抗生素有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係你呢d人搞到病菌有抗藥性 無抗生素用到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我真係痛左好耐<br />\n<br />\n我份工要講野搵食<br />\n<br />\npls help me<br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該停左剩低果兩次<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}